OL,5, Complaints made to the Energy Ombudsman
OL,6, by frustrated customers are at a record
OL,7, high, new data shows.                  
OL,9,FFigures shared with the BBC show       
OL,10,F105,340 complaints were received by the
OL,11,FOmbudsman in 2022, a jump of more than 
OL,12,F50% compared to two years before.      
OL,14,FThe data comes as energy suppliers are 
OL,15,Funder intense scrutiny over their      
OL,16,Fpractices amid rising bills.           
OL,18,FEnergy UK, which represents suppliers, 
OL,19,Fsaid the Ombudsman "plays an important 
OL,20,Frole" in resolving complex cases.      
